text:
Alright, look...I know I've said multiple times that I was having a bad day, and Gura made it better. It's a given really, shark is awesome. But today I was having a REALLY bad day; like, bad enough that not even most of the stream was enough to get me to really smile or laugh. At least...not until she told that foot story, at which point I absolutely LOST it. I laughed so hard I completely broke for a solid three minutes. 

Thank you, little shark; not just for being a special little goofball, but for being willing to tell us about things like that. It was a hilarious story, but it was obviously also super embarassing, and you talking about it with us really just feels like sharing silly stories in a cozy talk with a good friend. I know you might not feel the same way, Gura, but at least for me, it's a really special feeling, and I'm grateful for it every stream. If being a chumbuddy and a shrimp means I get to be friends with a radical shark like you, falling all this way down the rabbit hole was worth it.
